research_municipality_step.notes: The list of elected officials is primarily based on the Texas Municipal League (TML) City Officials Directory and confirmed by the official City of Panorama Village website. The Mayor and Mayor Pro Tem's terms are noted to expire in May 2026. While October 2024 meeting minutes listed Ted Nichols as a Councilmember in attendance, the TML directory, a dedicated list of officials with specific position numbers, does not include him and instead lists William Taylor for Council Position No. 3. The TML directory was prioritized for the structured list of officials and their designations.

office.name: Council Member - Mayor Pro Tempore - Position No. 2
